data.name: sqlSelectCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT p.pri_id, CASE WHEN ISNULL(p.is_co, 'F') = 'F' THEN CAST(p.pri_code AS varchar) ELSE CAST(mp.pri_code AS varchar) + '-' + CAST(p.pri_code AS varchar) END AS pri_code, c.CUSTOMER_CODE, c.NAME, p.pri_desc1, p.pri_site1, p.pri_name, p.pri_start_date, p.pri_est_completion_date, p.pri_completion_date, p.pri_type, p.pri_status, p.pri_division, p.prc_code, p.pri_whs, p.pri_billing_id, p.pri_ship_id, p.pri_desc, p.prcl_code, p.pri_holdback_pct, p.gst_code, p.sales_tax_id, p.next_po_seq, p.budget_frozen, p.username, p.pri_entry_date, p.USE_LEM_COMPONENTS, p.PRI_SHORT_NAME, p.pri_profit_center, p.close_acct_year, p.close_acct_period, p.customer_po, p.fuel_burden_recovery, p.MSP_Proj_ID, p.pri_is_schedule, p.pri_caps_status, p.sls_id, p.CapS_HasTaskError_TF, ISNULL(cn1.KnownAs, ISNULL(cn1.FirstName, '') + ' ' + ISNULL(cn1.LastName, '')) AS proj_manager, ISNULL(cn2.KnownAs, ISNULL(cn2.FirstName, '') + ' ' + ISNULL(cn2.LastName, '')) AS engineer, ISNULL(cn3.KnownAs, ISNULL(cn3.FirstName, '') + ' ' + ISNULL(cn3.LastName, '')) AS architect, ISNULL(cn4.KnownAs, ISNULL(cn4.FirstName, '') + ' ' + ISNULL(cn4.LastName, '')) AS field_forman, ISNULL(cn5.KnownAs, ISNULL(cn5.FirstName, '') + ' ' + ISNULL(cn5.LastName, '')) AS proj_accountant, ISNULL(cn6.KnownAs, ISNULL(cn6.FirstName, '') + ' ' + ISNULL(cn6.LastName, '')) AS estimator, ISNULL(cn7.KnownAs, ISNULL(cn7.FirstName, '') + ' ' + ISNULL(cn7.LastName, '')) AS salesperson, ISNULL(cn8.KnownAs, ISNULL(cn8.FirstName, '') + ' ' + ISNULL(cn8.LastName, '')) AS field_manager, rt.REV_DESC AS contract_type, CASE WHEN isnull(p.billing_level, '') = 'P' THEN 'Project' ELSE CASE WHEN isnull(p.billing_level, '') = 'L' THEN 'Level 1' ELSE CASE WHEN isnull(p.billing_level, '') = 'T' THEN 'Time Ticket' ELSE '' END END END AS Billing_Level, cat.prc_desc, RTRIM(CAST(cl.prcl_desc AS varchar(30))) AS prcl_desc, wh.description, gl.segment_desc, p.is_co, mp.pri_code AS master_code, mp.pri_name AS master_name, p.pri_code AS ProjectNumber, p.BaseFolder, p.pri_close_date, p.LandSubType FROM PROJ_HEADER AS p LEFT OUTER JOIN CUSTOMERS AS c ON c.CUSTOMER_ID = p.customer_id LEFT OUTER JOIN PROJ_CONTACTS AS pc ON pc.pri_id = p.pri_id INNER JOIN working_proj_selected AS w ON w.pri_id = p.pri_id LEFT OUTER JOIN web_strike_test.dbo.Contact AS cn1 ON cn1.ID = pc.proj_manager LEFT OUTER JOIN web_strike_test.dbo.Contact AS cn2 ON cn2.ID = pc.engineer LEFT OUTER JOIN web_strike_test.dbo.Contact AS cn3 ON cn3.ID = pc.architect LEFT OUTER JOIN web_strike_test.dbo.Contact AS cn4 ON cn4.ID = pc.field_forman LEFT OUTER JOIN web_strike_test.dbo.Contact AS cn5 ON cn5.ID = pc.proj_accountant LEFT OUTER JOIN web_strike_test.dbo.Contact AS cn6 ON cn6.ID = pc.estimator LEFT OUTER JOIN web_strike_test.dbo.Contact AS cn7 ON cn7.ID = pc.salesperson LEFT OUTER JOIN web_strike_test.dbo.Contact AS cn8 ON cn8.ID = pc.field_manager LEFT OUTER JOIN proj_cat AS cat ON cat.prc_code = p.prc_code LEFT OUTER JOIN proj_class AS cl ON cl.prcl_code = p.prcl_code LEFT OUTER JOIN WAREHOUSE AS wh ON wh.WHSE_ID = p.pri_whs LEFT OUTER JOIN GL_SEGMENT_SETUP AS gl ON gl.SEGMENT_VALUE = p.pri_division LEFT OUTER JOIN PROJ_HEADER AS mp ON mp.pri_id = p.CO_Pri_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN REVENUE_TYPES AS rt ON rt.REV_CODE = p.Contract_Type WHERE (w.username = @username)

data.name: sqlUpdateCommand1.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE [proj_header] SET [pri_code] = @pri_code, [pri_name] = @pri_name WHERE (([pri_id] = @Original_pri_id) AND ((@IsNull_pri_code = 1 AND [pri_code] IS NULL) OR ([pri_code] = @Original_pri_code)) AND ((@IsNull_pri_name = 1 AND [pri_name] IS NULL) OR ([pri_name] = @Original_pri_name))); SELECT pri_id, pri_code, pri_name FROM PROJ_HEADER WHERE (pri_id = @pri_id) ORDER BY pri_code

data.name: sqlDeleteCommand1.CommandText
data.value: DELETE FROM [proj_header] WHERE (([pri_id] = @Original_pri_id) AND ((@IsNull_pri_code = 1 AND [pri_code] IS NULL) OR ([pri_code] = @Original_pri_code)) AND ((@IsNull_pri_name = 1 AND [pri_name] IS NULL) OR ([pri_name] = @Original_pri_name)))

data.name: sqlInsertCommand2.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO [customers] ([customer_id], [customer_code], [name]) VALUES (@customer_id, @customer_code, @name); SELECT CUSTOMER_ID, CUSTOMER_CODE, NAME FROM CUSTOMERS WHERE (CUSTOMER_ID = @CUSTOMER_ID)

data.name: sqlUpdateCommand2.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE [customers] SET [customer_id] = @customer_id, [customer_code] = @customer_code, [name] = @name WHERE (([customer_id] = @Original_customer_id) AND ([customer_code] = @Original_customer_code) AND ((@IsNull_name = 1 AND [name] IS NULL) OR ([name] = @Original_name))); SELECT CUSTOMER_ID, CUSTOMER_CODE, NAME FROM CUSTOMERS WHERE (CUSTOMER_ID = @CUSTOMER_ID)

data.name: sqlSelectCommand10.CommandText
data.value: select distinct m.sls_id , isnull(s.firstname ,'') + case when isnull(s.firstname ,'') = '' then '' else ' ' end +isnull(s.lastname,'') [Salesperson] from TR_STRIKE_TEST10..mluser m join TR_STRIKE_TEST10..salespersons s on s.sls_id=m.sls_id where isnull(active,'F') = 'T' order by isnull(s.firstname ,'') + case when isnull(s.firstname ,'') = '' then '' else ' ' end +isnull(s.lastname,'')

data.name: sqlInsertCommand3.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO [warehouse] ([whse_id], [warehouse], [description]) VALUES (@whse_id, @warehouse, @description); SELECT WHSE_ID, WAREHOUSE, DESCRIPTION FROM WAREHOUSE WHERE (WHSE_ID = @WHSE_ID) ORDER BY DESCRIPTION

data.name: sqlUpdateCommand3.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE [warehouse] SET [whse_id] = @whse_id, [warehouse] = @warehouse, [description] = @description WHERE (([whse_id] = @Original_whse_id) AND ([warehouse] = @Original_warehouse) AND ((@IsNull_description = 1 AND [description] IS NULL) OR ([description] = @Original_description))); SELECT WHSE_ID, WAREHOUSE, DESCRIPTION FROM WAREHOUSE WHERE (WHSE_ID = @WHSE_ID) ORDER BY DESCRIPTION

data.name: sqlDeleteCommand9.CommandText
data.value: DELETE FROM [warehouse] WHERE (([whse_id] = @Original_whse_id) AND ([warehouse] = @Original_warehouse) AND ((@IsNull_description = 1 AND [description] IS NULL) OR ([description] = @Original_description)))

data.name: sqlSelectCommand14.CommandText
data.value: select c.id, isnull(c.knownas, isnull(c.firstname,'')+' '+isnull(c.lastname,'')) [Name], s.name [Supplier] from contact c join relations r on r.itemid=c.id and r.target='supplier' and r.itemtype='contact' join TR_STRIKE_TEST10..supplier_master s on s.supplier_id=r.targetid and r.target='supplier' and r.itemtype='contact' where c.type='Supplier' and c.id <> -1 and isnull(s.active,'F')='T' and r.companyid=15 and isnull(IsGenContractor,'F') = 'T' order by [Supplier],[Name]

data.name: sqlSelectCommand15.CommandText
data.value: select c.id, isnull(c.knownas, isnull(c.firstname,'')+' '+isnull(c.lastname,'')) [Name] from contact c join TR_STRIKE_TEST10..mluser m on m.contactid=c.id where type='User' and c.id <> -1 and isnull(estimator,'F') ='T' and isnull(m.inactive,'Y') = 'N' order by [Name]

data.name: sqlSelectCommand16.CommandText
data.value: select c.id, isnull(c.knownas, isnull(c.firstname,'')+' '+isnull(c.lastname,'')) [Name], cu.name [Customer] from contact c join relations r on r.itemid=c.id and r.target='customer' and r.itemtype='contact' join TR_STRIKE_TEST10..customers cu on cu.customer_id=r.targetid and r.target='customer' and r.itemtype='contact' where c.type='Customer' and c.id <> -1 and isnull(cu.active,'F')='T' and r.companyid=15 and isnull(active,'F')='T' order by [Customer],[Name]
